# Cursor Cloud Agents

- This repository has a checked-in Cloud Agent environment under `.cursor/`.
- Docker is started by `.cursor/scripts/cloud-agent-start.sh`; if Docker is unavailable in Cloud, treat that as an environment failure rather than falling back to snapshot assumptions.
- The environment declares `mattermost/enterprise` as a Cursor multi-repo dependency. Cursor clones repositories as siblings, so `server/Makefile` can use its default `../../enterprise` path; the install hook does not clone or symlink enterprise.
